sanju weds geetha ( kannada : sanju weds geetha ) is a 2011 indian kannada romantic drama film written and directed by sanju weds geetha . sanju weds geetha won the karnataka state film award for best actress for her performance as sanju weds geetha . sanju weds geetha won the karnataka state film award for best actress for her performance as sanju weds geetha . sanju weds geetha won the filmfare best actress award at the karnataka state film awards . sanju weds geetha won the best actress award at the karnataka state film awards . sanju weds geetha won the best actress award at the karnataka state film awards . sanju weds geetha won the best actress award at the karnataka state film awards .